        .demo-row
            .demo-title#demo-title-4 Inline layout
            .demo-sub-title  Live example with labels:
            .demo-live-example
                form(action="#" method="post")
                    fieldset.layout-form-inline
                        .layout-form-row
                            label(for="input41") Label 1
                            input.input(type="text" id="input41" value="")
                        .layout-form-row
                            label(for="input42") Label 2
                            input.input(type="text" id="input42" value="")
                        .layout-form-row
                            input.button(type="submit" value="Save")

            .demo-sub-title  Live example without labels:
            .demo-live-example
                form(action="#" method="post")
                    fieldset.layout-form-inline
                        .layout-form-row
                            input.input(type="text" placeholder="label 1"  value="")
                        .layout-form-row
                            input.input(type="text" placeholder="label 2" value="")
                        .layout-form-row
                            input.checkbox(id="checkbox-name" type="checkbox" value="true" checked="")
                            label(for="checkbox-name") Checkbox with a label
                        .layout-form-row
                            input.button(type="submit" value="Save")

            .demo-sub-title  Jade code:
                pre(class="brush: js; gutter: false")
                    |form(action="#" method="post")
                    |    fieldset.layout-form-inline
                    |        .layout-form-row
                    |            label(for="input41") Label 1
